stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Calculated
    Calculated --> Low : score < 30
    Calculated --> Medium : 30 <= score < 60
    Calculated --> High : 60 <= score < 80
    Calculated --> Critical : score >= 80
    Low --> Recalculated : New alert added
    Medium --> Recalculated
    High --> Recalculated
    Critical --> Recalculated
    Recalculated --> Calculated